MY FAV TIPS!⭐️⬇️
-

For my bougie girls who have been asking how to avoid damaging their manicure, here you go!💗

✅ When deadlifting/doing compound movements use straps to avoid breakage! 

✅ Don’t use your nails like a can opener, they are fragile(& expensive😭) use a coin or side of your thumb!

✅ lastly don’t use your nail to poke and prod at buttons and risk damage. Instead, use your knuckle. 

(Note: if u don’t like lifting with nails that’s fine!! 
But don’t be all up in here getting nasty abt it <3)
